to represent the interests
of my patient.

695
01:09:01,178 --> 01:09:03,138
- 你知道…
- 我可以与你单独谈谈吗？
- You <i>300--
-</i> Can I talk to you for a second?

696
01:09:03,138 --> 01:09:04,222
