如果你知道谁是控制你的人？
Can you see what it is
that's holding you prisoner?

756
01:14:21,957 --> 01:14:25,377
知道，是她
Yes, yes, she--

757
01:14:25,377 --> 01:14:27,087
告诉她，她必须和我说话！
Tell her she has
to talk to me!
Tell her!

758
01:14:28,421 --> 01:14:29,798
进来
Yes?

759
01:14:32,968 --> 01:14:35,387
