<i>What are you?</i>

777
01:15:54,049 --> 01:15:55,967
你为什么如此像人类，如此完美？
Why are you so human?
So perfect?

778
01:15:58,928 --> 01:16:00,805
什么飞船上的鸟人？
What are the bird creatures
on the ship?

779
01:16:00,805 --> 01:16:03,600
