I became the woman
I found there,

787
01:16:25,288 --> 01:16:27,165
在你思想最深处，你最需要的
in your deepest thoughts,
your deepest needs.

788
01:16:30,960 --> 01:16:34,255
我是你想像中的女人，卡尔森
I am the feminine
in your mind, Carlsen.

789
01:16:36,841 --> 01:16:38,635
Where are you?

790
01:16:40,178 --> 01:16:41,513
你在哪里？
Where are you!

791
01:16:42,889 --> 01:16:44,390
