I don't know.
Could the girl have been deliberately
leading us away from London?

815
01:19:25,802 --> 01:19:27,971
我们找得到全部受害者吗？
Is it possible we didn't find
all of her victims?

816
01:19:29,138 --> 01:19:30,473
