That's the difference between them
and their victims.

829
01:20:47,467 --> 01:20:49,218
受害人的灵魂不能离开他们的身体，
只有最初的三个能够做到
<i>The victims can't leave
their bodies.</i>
<i>Only the original three
can do that.</i>

830
01:20:51,512 --> 01:20:52,972
- 我已杀了他们其中的一个
- 什么其中一个？
But I've killed one of them.

831
01:20:53,931 --> 01:20:57,185
两个男吸血鬼中的一个
- One of which?
