<i>And she gave me
some of her energy.</i>

879
01:25:32,960 --> 01:25:35,880
当我们发现他们之前，
他们应该是彼此倚赖着生活
<i>They must have been living off
of each other when we found them.</i>

880
01:25:37,089 --> 01:25:39,050
他们只有三个留了下来
<i>There were only three
of them left.</i>

881
01:25:41,302 --> 01:25:43,137
她杀了我们的人，一个接一个
<i>She killed all of my men.</i>

882
01:25:44,513 --> 01:25:46,015
<i>One by one.</i>

883
01:25:47,516 --> 01:25:49,101
只有我幸存
<i>But I survived.</i>

884
01:25:50,227 --> 01:25:51,937
她想要我留下来，她选择了我！
<i>She wanted me to survive.</i>

885
01:25:53,147 --> 01:25:54,565
<i>She chose me!</i>

886
01:25:55,816 --> 01:25:58,319
为什么？为什么？
<i>Why, why!</i>

887
01:25:58,319 --> 01:26:01,697
她不是人类，她不是一个女人
Carlsen, she's not human,
she's not a woman.

888
01:26:01,697 --> 01:26:03,366
她会毁掉你
She'll destroy you.

889
01:26:05,618 --> 01:26:07,453
她会毁掉整个世界
She's destroyed worlds.

890
01:26:08,162 --> 01:26:09,789
有些事你应该想听，长官
There's something
you might want to hear, sir.

891
01:26:10,164 --> 01:26:12,124
英国广播公司的特别报道
A special bulletin
from the BBC.

892
01:26:13,125 --> 01:26:14,877
今晚，伦敦在毁灭的边缘…
<i>It's obvious that tonight,</i>

893
01:26:14,877 --> 01:26:18,214
自从闪击战以来，最严重的灾难
<i>London is on the brink of the worst
devastation since the blitz.</i>

894
01:26:18,214 --> 01:26:19,507
城市的大片区域在燃烧，完全不受控制
<i>From where I'm standing,</i>
<i>I can see large areas of the city
burning out of control.</i>

895
01:26:23,594 --> 01:26:26,889
成千上万的人正慌乱地经过街道
在混乱中，尽可能地逃难
<i>And thousands of people are now
rampaging through the streets here</i>
<i>in a frenzied last effort
to avoid the plague.</i>

896
01:26:30,226 --> 01:26:32,937
已经实施戒严三个多小时
<i>Martial law has been enforced now
for three hours</i>

897
01:26:32,937 --> 01:26:35,439
但显然无法阻止
<i>But for the moment,
it hasn't stemmed what is obviously...</i>

898
01:27:29,577 --> 01:27:31,203
- 我们一直在等你
- 谢谢，继续坚持
Yes, sir, we've been
expecting you.

899
01:27:31,203 --> 01:27:32,580
- 快点过去，警官
- 好的，长官
Thank you, carry on.
- Carry on, Sergeant.
- <i>Right, sir.</i>

900
01:27:34,582 --> 01:27:36,250
- 到那一边去
- 好的
- Hilggins, around the other side.
