<i>Sir, we have information regarding
the object in space,</i>

914
01:28:31,430 --> 01:28:33,015
- 是那个正在冲向地球的…
- 是的，先生
<i>which is bearing down on the Earth
at this moment--</i>
Ye-ye-yes, gentlemen, look, if you'll
excuse me just-- just for a moment.

915
01:28:34,059 --> 01:28:36,649
抱歉，请等一会

