<i>If we don't do as they say,
they'll shoot us out of the air.</i>

935
01:30:45,814 --> 01:30:49,276
零号，我是X射线318号，
请求清除障碍，请求着陆，完毕
Hello, zero, this is x-ray 3-1-8
requesting clearance to land-- over.

936
01:30:49,276 --> 01:30:52,237
