Come away from the aircraft.

938
01:31:04,333 --> 01:31:05,542
You are under quarantine.

939
01:31:07,461 --> 01:31:08,671
到这里来，长官
Over here, please, sir.

940
01:31:10,381 --> 01:31:12,633
不要过来！站在那里！
Don't come any closer,
stop there!

941
01:31:12,633 --> 01:31:14,885
