and what's going on.
No, not that I know of.

948
01:31:34,530 --> 01:31:36,740
- 有人听说过他吗？
- 没有
- Has anybody heard of him?
- No.

949
01:31:36,740 --> 01:31:38,117
他一定还在伦敦
Must still be in London.

950
01:31:38,784 --> 01:31:41,578
