<i>We have this
from General Ames in Brussels.</i>

961
01:32:21,076 --> 01:32:23,829
他将在三小时内做出决定
He's coming up
with that decision in...
Just under three hours.

962
01:32:25,998 --> 01:32:27,791
你知道与飞船有关的事吗？
Have you heard anything
about the ship?

963
01:32:27,791 --> 01:32:29,251
- 太空飞船？
